  "technicalDetails": "<p>Features:</p><ul><li>No dependencies on other paid cloud services</li><li>One time payment</li><li>The server can handle multiple clients at the same time</li><li>Easy to setup</li><li>No internet required</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Code Modules:</p><ul><li>VoskPlugin (Runtime)</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Number of Blueprints: 0</p><p>Number of C&#43;&#43; Classes: 2</p><p>Network Replicated: No</p><p>Supported Development Platforms: Windows, Mac, Linux</p><p>Supported Target Build Platforms: Windows, Mac, Linux</p><p><strong>Documentation:</strong> <a href=\"https://github.com/IlgarLunin/VoskPlugin-docs\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com/IlgarLunin/VoskPlugin-docs</a></p><p><strong>Discord:</strong> <a href=\"https://discord.gg/Tkf7xe2\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://discord.gg/Tkf7xe2</a></p>",
